short_description: This sandwich will help you conquer any morning.
product_description: Conquer every morning with Jimmy Dean English Muffin Sandwiches. Packed with 13 grams of protein per serving, our Sausage, Egg & Cheese English Muffin Sandwich gives you more fuel to power your morning. And if everyone has a great day, imagine all the good we can do. So let’s do it - let’s shine it forward and make this world a brighter place one breakfast sandwich at a time.

short_description: Rise and Shine: Start your morning off with a boost of happiness so good, you can taste it. Our snack size maple pancake sandwiches are made with savory, maple flavored sausage that will brighten anyone’s morning.

The Perfect Family Breakfast: Made with real ingredients and packed with 8 grams of protein, our sandwiches help you and the family wake up on a positive note. So, gather around the table and enjoy a warm and hearty breakfast every morning.
Never Miss Breakfast Again: Ready in just minutes, our breakfast sandwiches can conveniently be placed in the microwave and quickly heated. These hearty sandwiches make for the ideal meal.

Enjoy Just the Way You Want: Relish the bold taste of our breakfast sandwiches on their own, or try your favorite hot sauce to add a kick of heat to your morning! Add a side of fruit or yogurt for a sweet bite too.

Signature Sausage Since 1969: Since day one, we have worked hard to produce quality food that tastes as fresh as a country morning; because we know that for a lot of folks, a good start is all you need for a great day.
product_description: Enjoy breakfast any time of day with Jimmy Dean Frozen Snack Size Maple Pancake and Sausage Sandwiches. Includes 10 pancake sandwiches. Jimmy Dean once said, "Sausage is a great deal like life. You get out of it what you put in." Which pretty much sums up his magic formula for having a great day. Today, Jimmy Dean Brand brings you many ways to add some sunshine to your morning. Because today's your day to shine on.
